headline: S&P 500 Dashboard And Measuring The Large Cap Bias With EQWL
summary: Invesco S&P 100 Equal Weight ETF has outperformed RSP for two years, pointing to a recent large cap bias in the S&P 500. Click for a review of EQWL and more.
